  <code>
    x = {"name"=> "fiona", "breed"=> "king charles cavelier", "hobby"=> "napping all day"}
  </code>
  <br></br>
  <li>Example2</li><p>How about if I want to retrieve the value for breed?</p>
  <code>
    x["breed"]<br>
    king charles cavelier
  </code>
  </li>
